c: 12
v: 109
t: "Kandi mbere yawe nta bandi twigeze twohereza ngo tubahishurire ubutumwa, usibye ko babaga ari abagabo bakomoka mu midugudu (twabaga tuboherejemo). Ese ntibatambagira isi ngo barebe uko iherezo (ry’abahakanyi) bababanjirije ryagenze? Kandi ubuturo bw’imperuka ni bwo bwiza kuri babandi batinya Allah. Ese nta bwenge mugira"